    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tropical forests with an upper story of deciduous trees and a lower story of evergreen, located in areas having a longer dry season than a seasonal rainforest.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
